short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Resume your YouTube subscriptions with a single click.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
On click of the Resume YouTube Subs extension icon your YouTube subscriptions will be opened in a new tab and the extension will automatically scroll to the newest watched video.

To report issues visit https://github.com/michael-schaller/resume-youtube-subs/issues/new/choose.

To get more details about this extension visit https://github.com/michael-schaller/resume-youtube-subs.
